I".	<p>I enjoy learning new things. This includes technology, physical skills and learning new sports. A few of the outdoor activities I enjoy include downhill skateboarding, surfing, snowboarding, mountain-biking, rock-climbing &amp; sailing. I also enjoy photography and videography.
I love reading and try to read a few books every month, usually a mix of fiction and non-fiction.</p>

